:The 'material' properties on the [[Part_Feature]] page are of two distinct types: Materials::PropertyMaterial (Data tab) and App::PropertyMaterial (View tab). The first is defined by the Material Workbench, but can also include visual material properties. The second is defined by core and only contains visual material properties. This is not necessarily very clear when you read the Part_Feature page (we leave out the "*::Property" prefix when we list properties).
